beer.beer_description:
Citra is a US grown hop and the first in our Varietal Hop IPA series.
We just love Citra at The Little Brewing Company. It is the workhorse in the brewery, finding favour in nearly all our IPAs.
A little beer is good.
HOP VARIETY: Citra
HOP AROMA: Citrus,grapefruit,lime,melon and passionfruit.

Load up those hops, watch the IBU grow and drink it down! Now youre all hopped up. The more bitter, the better. That's 35 different beers with an IBU of 65 or higher. Try 5 more for Level 8!
